name: Higher Ed Gender Gap
title: Gender Disparity in Tertiary Education
description: In 2023, only 45.15% of women aged 25 and above in Honduras have completed short-cycle tertiary education, compared to 47.08% of men. This highlights a gender disparity in higher education attainment.

name: Low Tertiary Completion
title: Low Tertiary Education Completion Rate
description: As of 2023, only 46.02% of the population aged 25 and above in Honduras have completed short-cycle tertiary education, indicating a need for improvement in higher education access and completion.
